    Use Collections.EMPTY_MAP on J2SE 1.3 or later.

    @Deprecated
public class EmptyMap
extends Object
implements Map, Cloneable
    Read-only empty map. remove(Object), clear() and putAll(Map) with an empty Map as parameter are supported operations (and do nothing) since FreeMarker 2.3.20.
